            "body": "I need to refactor my setup a bit. \n\nI had to comment out `persistence` plugin load on UIENTER to fix the issue\n\n\nRemoved following callback from my dotfiles:\n``` \n\n-- Fixes snacks : https://github.com/folke/snacks.nvim/issues/1308\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd(\"UIEnter\", {\n  nested = true,\n  callback = function(ev)\n    vim.cmd(\"silent %bw!\")\n    vim.cmd(\"silent clearjumps\")\n    require(\"persistence\").load()\n  end,\n})\n```",
